# <%= current_page.data.title %>

Weight Loss Plan helps make healthier food choices, set weight loss goals to helps users get more active and burn more calories.

The app follows the [standard pattern](documentation/guides/standard-pattern). It uses a Static Assets S3 bucket to pull information using its "Calorie Search" function. The name of this bucket is hardcoded into the mobile app which makes replacing it more difficult.

